data.description: Exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in the heart of Spokane. Overflowing with natural light, the main floor houses two generously sized bedrooms ideal for guests and an open-concept living and dining area! You will love the updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances & ample cabinet/counter space making it a culinary haven. Extra eating space at the bar adds versatility for meals and gatherings. Downstairs, the lower level greets you with a sense of spaciousness and convenience - large primary boasts a walk-in closet and a connected bathroom, offering privacy to homeowners. Additional bonus room and laundry room also on the lower level! Added features include a newer furnace and AC unit from 2020 & tastefully updated bathrooms that enhance the home's modern appeal. Outside features spacious deck, paver patio and raised garden. This property is a perfect combination of style and functionality, offering a welcoming living space to enjoy. Conveniently located near schools, parks, dining and shopping!
